furniture, appliances,

194
00:09:38,050 --> 00:09:41,290
or some steamy watercolor rat erotica.

195
00:09:41,369 --> 00:09:45,170
I'm just describing what most
people did in 2020.

196
00:09:45,930 --> 00:09:49,090
